			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=449&amp;sid=5df381c87e5bc54b45cdfcac6fbda21c#p449"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=449&amp;sid=5df381c87e5bc54b45cdfcac6fbda21c#p449" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#1</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2&amp;sid=5df381c87e5bc54b45cdfcac6fbda21c" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Jordan Tuwiner</a></strong> &raquo; September 16th, 2010, 8:28 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

