			<div class="content"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Bell's current stat line includes a 50/2 K/BB ratio and a .539 OPS. Do we let him open 2011 at 3B or should we look into a free agent 3B option? <br /><br />If I'm the Orioles, I send Bell back to Norfolk and resign Wigginton to a one year contract to hold down 3B for at least the first half of the season. Hopefully Wigginton produces like he did last year and the Orioles flip him for something before the deadline.<!-- google_ad_section_end --></div>
